### Get All Products
GET http://localhost:5001/api/v1/products
Content-Type: application/json


### Get Products by Category
GET http://localhost:5001/api/v1/products?categoryId={{category_id}}&page=1&limit=10
Content-Type: application/json

### Search Products with Filters
GET http://localhost:5001/api/v1/products?search=Latte&type=SIMPLE&isActive=true&sortBy=basePrice&sortOrder=asc
Content-Type: application/json

### Get Products by Category with Search and Filters
GET http://localhost:5001/api/v1/products?categoryId={{category_id}}&search=Latte&type=SIMPLE&isActive=true&sortBy=basePrice&sortOrder=asc
Content-Type: application/json


### Get product by slug
GET http://localhost:5001/api/v1/products/yogurt-trai-cay
Content-Type: application/json


### Create a new product (with image upload)
POST http://localhost:5001/api/v1/internal/products
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=boundary

--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="sku"

TIRA-005
--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="name"

Flat White Image
--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="type"

SIMPLE
--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="basePrice"

135000
--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="taxRate"

0.08
--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="category"

{ "id": "{{category_id}}" }
--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="sortOrder"

2
--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="optionGroups"

[{"optionGroupId": "{{option_group_id}}", "sortOrder": 1, "optionValues": [{"optionId": "{{option_id}}", "price": 20000}]}]
--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="image"; filename="coffee.jpg"
Content-Type: image/jpeg

< ./coffee.jpg
--boundary--

### Create a new product (JSON - legacy/no image)
POST http://localhost:5001/api/v1/internal/products
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

{
    "sku": "TIRA-003",
    "name": "Flat Black",
    "type": "SIMPLE",
    "basePrice": 130000,
    "taxRate": 0.5,
    "category": {
        "id": "{{category_id}}"
    },
    "sortOrder": 1,
    "optionGroups": [  
        {
            "optionGroupId": "{{option_group_id}}", //OptionGroup table
            "sortOrder": 1,
            "optionValues": [
                {
                    "optionId": "{{option_id}}", // ProductOption table
                    "price": 20000
                }
            ]
        }
    ]
}
### Create Option Group & Options
POST http://localhost:5001/api/v1/internal/option-groups
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

{
    "name": "Sugar Level",
    "isRequired": true,
    "isMultiple": false,
    "sortOrder": 1,
    "options": [
        {
            "name": "Sugar 50%",
            "basePrice": 0,
            "sortOrder": 1
        },
        {
            "name": "Sugar 70%",
            "basePrice": 0,
            "sortOrder": 2
        }
    ]
}

PUT /api/v1/internal/products/{{product_id}}/option-groups/{{option_group_id}}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}
   
 {
    "sortOrder": 2,
    "optionValues": [
        {
          "optionId": "{{option_id_1}}",
          "price": 15000
        },
        {
            "optionId": "{{option_id_2}}",
            "price": 25000
        }
    ]
 }

### Update product details
PUT http://localhost:5001/api/v1/internal/products/9eb242d4-7db9-4329-87e8-9c56b4408ac3
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "Updated Product Name",
    "basePrice": 150000,
    "description": "Updated description for the product"
}

### Update product image
PUT http://localhost:5001/api/v1/internal/products/{{product_id}}
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=boundary

--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="name"

Updated Product with Image
--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="image"; filename="new_coffee.jpg"
Content-Type: image/jpeg

< ./new_coffee.jpg
--boundary--

### Delete product
DELETE http://localhost:5001/api/v1/internal/products/9eb242d4-7db9-4329-87e8-9c56b4408ac3
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}


### Get All Products (Admin) - no isActive filter, returns all
GET http://localhost:5001/api/v1/internal/admin/products?page=1&limit=10
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

### Get All Products (Admin) - with isActive filter explicitly
GET http://localhost:5001/api/v1/internal/admin/products?isActive=true&page=1&limit=10
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

### Toggle Product Active (Internal - Manager/Admin)
PATCH http://localhost:5001/api/v1/internal/products/PRODUCT_ID_HERE/toggle-active
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

### Toggle Product Active (Admin only)
PATCH http://localhost:5001/api/v1/internal/admin/products/PRODUCT_ID_HERE/toggle-active
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}


